{"tid":800791,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲可以有人話咩性格、內在美最重要既廢話??","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T08:05:26.000Z","uid":204717,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbe1856d2671d644825926561e81a2e71ea0024","tid":800791,"uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"連咩女神/男神外表但公主港女/花心狗公性格會無人要既廢話都講得出 <br />\n<strong>有個女神/男神樣理撚得你咩性格都大把男人/女人狗衝啦 <br />\n如果唔係佢點會公主得起 花生得起啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">調返轉比個細眼闊臉鄂突鼻大豬扒你 <br />\n全世界最好人性格又有咩用? </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根本稍微有智慧既人 <br />\n就算係小學生開始都識得知道 <br />\n擺出咩姿態黎迎合人係對自己最好既選擇 <br />\n<br />\n一個人靚但性格差恰人憎 咁係顯示佢蠢多過佢性格真係差 <br />\n一個人靚但性格超好人 咁係顯示佢聰明 <br />\n識得擺出最合適既姿態拓展自己既優勢多過佢性格真係好 <br />\n<br />\n根本乜柒性格都好 對住任何人 <br />\n只要有心隨時都可以變換 <br />\n<br />\n點解有人到今日都仲可以打哂飛機話咩性格比外表重要?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個人既組成部分 <br />\n除左自我意識果部分-理性 <br />\n好明仲有一份動物性既-本能 <br />\n<br />\n一個人係由<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">理性+本能</span></strong>組成 <br />\n但永遠人都想逃避本能 最動物性果部分 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明係動物又唔敢承認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以先會由細到大教你打哂飛機咩: <br />\n「內在美最重要。」 「性格好最重要。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你連本能果部分都滿足唔到仲講乜撚野理性乜野高級既情感 <br />\n你連野都食唔飽仲講乜撚做其他野???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n滿足到本能果部分先再教人呢啲真善美啦戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"153ac69f9f0cb8ef0e797c7d1f87ad8c576f425b","tid":800791,"uid":204717,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:57:37.000Z","msg":"對住啲醜男豬扒又係咁教 <br />\n對住啲男神女神又係咁教 <br />\n<br />\n好啦 到醜男豬扒接觸到現實 <br />\n又喊屎喊忽話世界唔公平 <br />\n屌乜柒人好膚淺 <br />\n<br />\n問題係而家只有一部分人可以有條件滿足果份本能啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你呢個扭曲社會就本住咩人人平等咁去教 <br />\n人生而不平等又唔敢承認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>就好似動人愛情電影故事換左醜男豬扒/稍微無咁靚既男女主角做 <br />\n成個觀感都會大打折扣 比人話選角失敗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解?因為滿足唔到產生果份高級感情(理性)既種子(本能)囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>人愈逃避自己係動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愈唔敢面對自己既本能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n問題同悲劇就永遠都唔可能解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723acdf179aa3798e300399cc54d6de91c9222d1","tid":800791,"uid":204717,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:04:32.000Z",